                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-76-off394 t18250113-76-cd395"></join>, a saddle, value 3 l.; a bridle, value 1 l., and a martingale, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18250113-76-victim439" type="victimName">
                  James 
                  Cranston
               <interp inst="t18250113-76-victim439" type="surname" value="Cranston"></interp>
